                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <h4>Ben Morrison</h4>
                            <p>Managing Director, Morrison Civil Contractors</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-industry">Civil Contracting</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
                            <p>
                                "The strategic approach to our working capital requirements was exactly what our 
                                electrical business needed. Professional service, transparent communication, and 
                                funding that supports our growth rather than constraining it."
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <h4>Lisa Thompson</h4>
                            <p>Director, Thompson Industrial Electrical</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-industry">Industrial Electrical</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
