                                "From initial consultation to funding approval, the process was streamlined and professional. 
                                Their industry knowledge of commercial plumbing helped secure optimal terms for our 
                                commercial property purchase."
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <h4>Mark Hughes</h4>
                            <p>Owner, Hughes Commercial Plumbing</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-industry">Commercial Trades</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Why Choose EVFBS -->
        <section class="why-choose">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Why Australian Business Builders Choose EVFBS</h2>
                <div class="benefits-grid">
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>Strategic Partnership Approach</h3>
                        <p>We're not just a finance broker – we're your strategic partner committed to long-term business success and growth.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>Commercial Trades Expertise</h3>
                        <p>Deep specialization in commercial trades, civil contractors, and industrial businesses with exclusion of high-risk residential building.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>Technology-Enhanced Service</h3>
                        <p>AI-driven analytics provide superior insights and recommendations for optimal finance structure and strategic planning.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>Professional Assessment</h3>
                        <p>Comprehensive evaluation process ensures finance solutions align with your business goals, capacity, and growth objectives.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>Transparent Communication</h3>
                        <p>Clear, professional communication throughout the entire process with no hidden fees or surprise conditions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>ASIC Compliant Service</h3>
                        <p>Licensed and compliant service delivery meeting all regulatory requirements and professional standards for your protection.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Ready to Begin Your Strategic Finance Partnership?</h2>
                <p>Join hundreds of Australian business builders who've transformed their growth trajectory through our professional finance solutions.</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/get-quote" class="primary-button large">Request Professional Assessment</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="secondary-button large">Start the Conversation</a>
